# Tinderbox Install

1. Setup a fresh Gentoo system
2. Create some directories:
   * /etc/portage/package.mask
   * /var/cache/tinderbox
   * /var/...
3. Copy make.tinderbox.conf and bashrc to /etc/portage
4. cd /root; git clone git://git.overlays.gentoo.org/proj/flameeyes-tinderbox.git tinderbox
5. ./tinderbox-continuous.sh

# make.tinderbox.conf
SYNC, EMERGE_DEFAULT_OPTS, MAKEOPTS
